spec_data.Name: python-amqplib
spec_data.Description:
Client library for AMQP (Advanced Message Queuing Protocol)

Supports the 0-8 AMQP spec, and has been tested with RabbitMQ
and Python's 2.4, 2.5, and 2.6.
